         <OBJECT_CONTRACT>
            <TITLE>
               <P>Provision of catering services at Hackney’s Professional Development Centre</P>
            </TITLE>
            <REFERENCE_NUMBER>DN309101</REFERENCE_NUMBER>
            <CPV_MAIN>
               <CPV_CODE CODE="55500000"/>
            </CPV_MAIN>
            <TYPE_CONTRACT CTYPE="SERVICES"/>
            <SHORT_DESCR>
               <P>The London Borough of Hackney is seeking to contract with an experienced supplier to provide high-quality event catering and cafeteria service to The Tomlinson Centre, Hackney’s professional development centre. This shall include beverages and refreshments, platter and cafeteria lunches and occasionally banqueting services.</P>
               <P>The Tomlinson Centre is a professional training and development centre belonging to Hackney Council which provides education and conferencing facilities across a range of disciplines. Its facilities are also rented to a wide range of organisations. It is under the management of Hackney Learning Trust, the Council’s education department.</P>
               <P>The contract period shall be 2 years, commencing in June 2018, with the option for two annual extensions thereafter.</P>
            </SHORT_DESCR>
            <VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL CURRENCY="GBP">700000</VAL_ESTIMATED_TOTAL>
            <NO_LOT_DIVISION/>
            <OBJECT_DESCR ITEM="1">
               <CPV_ADDITIONAL>
                  <CPV_CODE CODE="55523000"/>
               </CPV_ADDITIONAL>
               <n2016:NUTS CODE="UKI41"/>
               <SHORT_DESCR>
                  <P>The Contractor shall provide a high-quality event catering and cafeteria service to The Tomlinson Centre. This shall include beverages and refreshments, platter and cafeteria lunches and occasionally banqueting services.</P>
                  <P>The meeting room catering service shall be available between 08:00 – 16:00. Meeting room lunches shall be required between the hours of 12:00 and 14:00. The café service shall be available between 08:00 – 16:00 with lunch being served between the hours of 12:00 and 14:00.</P>
                  <P>The contractors should show flexibility and be able to respond to any ad hoc requests outside of these core lunch hours.</P>
                  <P>Below are the average annual number of:</P>
                  <P>Beverages - 31500.</P>
                  <P>Cafeteria lunches - 6500.</P>
                  <P>Finger buffets - 1500.</P>
                  <P>Sandwich lunches - 3000.</P>
               </SHORT_DESCR>
               <AC_PROCUREMENT_DOC/>
               <VAL_OBJECT CURRENCY="GBP">700000</VAL_OBJECT>
               <DURATION TYPE="MONTH">24</DURATION>
               <NO_RENEWAL/>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <OPTIONS/>
               <OPTIONS_DESCR>
                  <P>Following the initial 2 year term, there will be an option for 2 annual extensions to the contract thereafter. Renewal will be agreed at least 12 weeks prior to the contract end date or extension end date.</P>
               </OPTIONS_DESCR>
               <NO_EU_PROGR_RELATED/>
            </OBJECT_DESCR>
         </OBJECT_CONTRACT>
